io.doov.core.dsl.field.types

Interface TemporalFieldInfo<N extends java.time.temporal.Temporal>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - the type of the field value
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseFieldInfo<N>, DslField<N>, Readable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DateIsoFieldInfo, LocalDateFieldInfo, LocalDateTimeFieldInfo, LocalTimeFieldInfo, TimeIsoFieldInfo

    public interface TemporalFieldInfo<N extends java.time.temporal.Temporal>
extends BaseFieldInfo<N>
    Base interface for temporal field info.

    It contains default methods for common checks, which are calls to methods on TemporalCondition.
